|z|\geq\max\{|\operatorname{Re}z|,|\operatorname{Im}z|\}
2|z|\geq |\operatorname{Re}z|+|\operatorname{Im}z|.
z=x+iy
x=\operatorname{Re}z
y=\operatorname{Im}z
(\sqrt{2}|z|)^2=2|z|^2=2x^2+2y^2.
(|\operatorname{Re}z|+|\operatorname{Im}z|)^2=(|x|+|y|)^2=x^2+y^2+2|xy|.
(\sqrt{2}|z|)^2-(|\operatorname{Re}z|+|\operatorname{Im}z|)^2=x^2+y^2-2|xy|=(|x|-|y|)^2\geq 0
\sqrt{2}|z|\geq |\operatorname{Re}z|+|\operatorname{Im}z|
|\operatorname{Re}z|=|\operatorname{Im}z|
